          "latency_ms": 7691,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "While collective redress mechanisms enhance consumer protection, qualified representative actions should remain well-structured and predictable to avoid excessive litigation that could undermine legal clarity and business stability.",
